st variable type annotations\\\\\\\" we have. It might be helpful to inspect the git diff to see changes made. I wonder if this will give me a clearer picture of the different types we use. Let's dive into it and see what I find, as it might help clarify how variable types are being handled.\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_cuBp03uL3lNW900wrTnCPan6|fc_07804db651c470730169faf9ab82248193b4d46741fc90da59\", \"name\": \"bash\", \"arguments\": {\"command\": \"git diff -- tests/src/org.tpolecat/doobie-core_3/0.13.4/src/test/scala/org_tpolecat/doobie_core_3/TransactorInnerTransactorInnerFromDriverManagerTest.scala\"}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1800, \"output\": 820, \"cacheRead\": 23552, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 26172, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1778055580886, \"responseId\": \"resp_07804db651c470730169faf99d53c881939dc4fd8c33e9e69b\"}}\n1319:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_cuBp03uL3lNW900wrTnCPan6|fc_07804db651c470730169faf9ab82248193b4d46741fc90da59\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"(no output)\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1778055599506}}\n1320:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_cuBp03uL3lNW900wrTnCPan6|fc_07804db651c470730169faf9ab82248193b4d46741fc90da59\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"(no output)\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1778055599506}}\n1321:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"**Evaluating class naming and issues**\\n\\nI'm considering a name like \\\"TransactorInnerFromDriverManagerTest\\\" since the package object \\\"transactor\\